      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed, and treated like royalty. It\u2019s in truly impeccable condition, inside and out; you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and looks it, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
