    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero imperfections, having been meticulously garage-kept and hand-washed since day one. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and aromatic, free from any creases or signs of wear, while every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach; the engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with seamless precision, and the service history is documented to the mile. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a flawlessly preserved example that looks, smells, and drives like a brand-new machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
